(175, 'Sadhana Shrestha', 'whitepearllight@gmail.com', '9779803463278', 'Hi there,\nGreetings!!\n\nI would like to draw your attention towards our company where we provide essential workers in different sectors.\n\nI&#39;m Sadhana Shrestha, International Coordinator  of White Pearl Light Manpower Pvt. Ltd. a company which is based on recruiting candidates.\n\nFirst, let me tell you about our company. White Pearl Light Pvt. Ltd., is one of the reputed manpower agencies and exporters established in Nepal and approved by the Ministry of Labor, Government of Nepal, with Registration No. 1125/073/74 dated 15th March 2017. Also, it has been affiliated with the Nepal Association of Foreign Employment Agencies (NAFEA) as a General Member. We are enjoying an excellent reputation worldwide, engaged in providing manpower services since 1996 through the issuance of registration certificates introduced by the Government of Nepal.\n\nIt has been many years since we are recruiting candidates from Nepal and Dubai and sending them to the middle east and Europe. We can provide highly-skilled, skilled, semi-skilled, and unskilled workers based on the relevant works.\n\nIf you are interested in hiring workers from Nepal, please share the requirements with your terms and conditions.\n\nLooking Forward to hearing from you soon.\nAny feedback you can give me on this would be highly appreciated.\n\nThank you.\n\nBest regards\nSadhana Shrestha\nInternational Coordinator\nWhatsApp: 9779803463278', NULL, '2021-03-25 04:08:39', '2021-03-25 04:08:39'),
